{"tid":386773,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"公屋根本唔應該存在","createTime":"2017-09-04T06:51:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T07:43:03.000Z","uid":13969,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d20a2d015224d67f4a5d4fc3c21bcd88654e49b","tid":386773,"uid":13969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:51:37.000Z","msg":"文有少少長，為左香港好，大家睇睇<br />\n公屋個制度垃撚圾就係人都知<br />\n濫用等等既情況嚴重到仆街<br />\n浪費極多社會資源<br />\n甚至有公屋仲靚過居屋<br />\n憑咩撚野<br />\n我個人建議將公屋數量減少<br />\n轉做起更靚既居屋<br />\n將居屋用成本既價格賣出去<br />\n多出來既錢起更靚既居屋<br />\n起碼會令大家有心有力去儲錢買樓<br />\n而唔係<br />\n等公屋/租樓<br />\n得兩個咁撚on9既出路"},{"pid":"bce780b568402161d9d11fb43b7b2825be77ff1a","tid":386773,"uid":126293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:52:35.000Z","msg":"長 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e948d87581d3bed0d18d11394c48daea962bc61f","tid":386773,"uid":13969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:54:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>長 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講住咁多先<br />\n唔想大家睇都唔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db47447f737a864ff12259c577ae88f16878d41","tid":386773,"uid":7942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:55:45.000Z","msg":"又係到鳩嗡，講咁撚多做乜，直接中央分配啦，都唔明點解今日今日，阿豬阿狗都話買樓，無本事無運氣咪認命囉，硬係要拉埋置業係必需嚟講，居住就必需，置業唔係囉"},{"pid":"6eec7d96dc62722bfed3a902fa05f38ac7879597","tid":386773,"uid":13969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:00:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係到鳩嗡，講咁撚多做乜，直接中央分配啦，都唔明點解今日今日，阿豬阿狗都話買樓，無本事無運氣咪認命囉，硬係要拉埋置業係必需嚟講，居住就必需，置業唔係囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你覺得大部人都係阿豬阿狗？<br />\n有邊個唔想用一個合理既價格係香港買合理既樓<br />\n而且我無表達置業係必須<br />\n呢個世界唔係得有錢同無錢<br />\n仲有中產<br />\n仲有肯返工儲到百幾萬既人<br />\n跳出去啦<br />\n關中央撚事咩<br />\n極端撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7cf8e8c61c256e288d474d91e3afd133a9868f","tid":386773,"uid":13969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:01:55.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"085046543ce58a11de30e5ac3ee2f86562c4c0ef","tid":386773,"uid":13969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:34:24.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"f48e3ca76b52dcd249c5b766a5b0152f7063e40d","tid":386773,"uid":13969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:34:34.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"bfd84af9ca1003de2b2a15f30612301e1e9a073f","tid":386773,"uid":13969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:34:44.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"30d3f8f5a379476e2ee2d7ebf5ddddb967e525f5","tid":386773,"uid":13969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:34:55.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"9fa9aeb8ec84cba0a45346bcae9aa3b8321169ec","tid":386773,"uid":13969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:35:05.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"5500e483907ff494ef7ae3b91a1e388659b4ccb8","tid":386773,"uid":13969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:35:22.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"80050f8dc7b2f880c3d5b3f09090a0ea9d14470f","tid":386773,"uid":13969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:35:35.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"a8fa53fecb8f823056904faf44e22c5f8398e056","tid":386773,"uid":13969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:35:46.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"b21ef4ed98b989c561e97763d9abebbed9c5978d","tid":386773,"uid":13969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:35:56.000Z","msg":"10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9da5e2df28862c88ac7092808513362a8ce46ab","tid":386773,"uid":13969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:36:47.000Z","msg":"11"},{"pid":"838e63af2ca6bb7950921acd6e482fb27292453b","tid":386773,"uid":13969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:38:00.00